Do you know Vancouver offers unique Staycation ideas?

Yes, that’s right. In your backyard is a vibrant and breathtaking city, which is precisely why we put together a list of fun staycation activities on our blog. 

Explore fun activities only minutes away and within easy walking distance from Waterfront Bombay Brow Bar.

For a limited time only, Bombay Waterfront offers 15% off brow and beauty services for first-time guests. 

Book your appointment ahead of time with code WATERFRONT15, and make it part of your Vancouver Staycation plans! 

🌟 And don’t forget to enter our “Bombay Bestie” Contest. You and a friend could be the lucky winners of an Ultimate Spa Day at our Waterfront location! 

Check our website for our blog post as well more info on our Bombay Bestie Contest.
